  "summary": "Jose Manuel Amado Abelenda is a Galician entrepreneur and sports industry executive based in the A Coruña/Oleiros area of Galicia, Spain. He served as President of the Clúster Galego da Industria do Deporte e o Benestar from June 2022 to January 2025 and currently remains on its board as a Vogal. He is the sole administrator and founder of Motivos Singulares S.L., co-founder of Xenese Iniciativas, and founder of Serviocio S.L., with a career spanning more than 21 registered companies in Spain's Boletín Oficial del Registro Mercantil (BORME). He holds a degree in Physical Activity and Sports Sciences from INEF de Galicia.",
